    {
      "h2": "Service animal relief areas",
      "h3s": [
        "Contact us or provide feedback",
        "Additional accessibility information and policies"
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Service Animal Relief Areas (SARAs) are available at all terminals for service animals and pets. These areas include indoor and outdoor spaces with features like artificial grass, sinks, and waste stations to keep things clean and comfortable.",
        "We want every traveler at JFK to feel welcome and supported. If you have questions about accessibility or want to share feedback, we are here to listen.",
        "You can use our feedback form to send comments or suggestions about your experience at JFK Airport.",
        "For accessibility-related questions, you can email us.",
        "If you need to reach our ADA/Section 504 Coordinator & Title VI/Non-Discrimination Coordinator, contact AVIADA@panynj.gov",
        "Nondiscrimination Poster (PDF) opens in a new tab",
        "Americans with Disabilities Act (ADA) Information opens in a new tab",
        "Title VI Information opens in a new tab",
        "Port Authority’s Reasonable Modification Policy (PDF) opens in a new tab"
      ],
